Sentencas: Gadolinium doped ceria (Ce0.8Gd0.2O2 _ x-CGO) layer fabricated by spray pyrolysis is investigated as the diffusion barrier for solid oxide fuel cell.
Titulo: Spray pyrolysis of doped-ceria barrier layers for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: It is deposited between the La0.6Sr0.4FeO3-8 cathode and the yttria stabilized zirconia electrolyte to mitigate harmful interdiffusion of elements.
Titulo: Spray pyrolysis of doped-ceria barrier layers for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The parameters of the fabrication process are linked to the measured area specific resistances of the symmetrical cells and the efficiency of the fuel cells.
Titulo: Spray pyrolysis of doped-ceria barrier layers for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Results show, that application of 800 nm thick barrier effectively hinder negative reactions, while 400 nm thick layer is sufficient to prevent degradation of the Ohmic resistance.
Titulo: Spray pyrolysis of doped-ceria barrier layers for solid oxide fuel cells
